OL,3,CMan jailed for life for murder of two-
OL,4,Cyear-old son
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for life for the
OL,7,Fmurder of his two-year-old son in
OL,8,FBlackpool.
OL,10,FDaniel Hardcastle killed Damion
OL,11,FRussell in a "brutal and sustained
OL,12,Fassault" at their home in Central
OL,13,FDrive, Blackpool in August 2023.
OL,15,FHardcastle claimed the toddler had
OL,16,Finjured himself after falling and
OL,17,Fhitting his head on a coffee table.
OL,19,FBut a pathologist found the extensive
OL,20,Finjuries suffered by the little boy
OL,21,Fwere inconsistent with that claim.
