OL,3,CMan jailed for life for murder of two-
OL,4,Cyear-old son
OL,6,F31-year-old Hardcastle was found
OL,7,Fguilty of murder after a four-week
OL,8,Ftrial at Preston Crown Court. The jury
OL,9,Ftook just two hours to reach their
OL,10,Funanimous verdict.
OL,12,FThe trial heard that Damion had
OL,13,Fsuffered horrendous injuries including
OL,14,Fa forceful adult human bite mark to
OL,15,Fhis upper right thigh. He had also
OL,16,Fsuffered fractured ribs, bruising
OL,17,Facross his whole body and a tear to
OL,18,Fthe inside of his lip consistent with
OL,19,Fa drinking bottle being forced into
OL,20,Fhis mouth.
