OL,4,Cyear-old son
OL,6,FThe jury were told Hardcastle, who had
OL,7,Fsole care of his son, had started
OL,8,Fdrinking more in the days and weeks
OL,9,Fbefore the assault.
OL,11,FHe had isolated himself from his
OL,12,Fsupport network and the night
OL,13,Fimmediately before inflicting the
OL,14,Finjuries which ultimately killed
OL,15,FDamion, Hardcastle spent all night
OL,16,Fchatting to a woman he had met online.
