OL,3,CMan jailed for life for murder of two-
OL,4,Cyear-old son
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Al Davies,
OL,7,FLancashire Police said: "First and
OL,8,Fforemost my thoughts today are with
OL,9,FDamion's loved ones. I hope this
OL,10,Fsentence gives them some sense that
OL,11,Fwhile nothing can bring Damion back
OL,12,Fthat justice has been done for their
OL,13,Floved one.
OL,15,F"Damion's murder was an unspeakably
OL,16,Fvile and heinous act committed by the
OL,17,Fvery man Damion should have been able
OL,18,Fto rely upon to love and protect him `
OL,19,Fhis own father."
